text: Nizhniye Khomyaki () is a rural locality (a village) in Vereshchaginskoye Urban Settlement, Vereshchaginsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 5 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 4.5 km south from Vereshchagino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Vereshchaginsky District
title: Nizhniye Khomyaki
